sentences.english: In many ways synthetic fibers are much better than natural fibers.
sentences.chinese: 在许多方面，合成纤维比天然纤维好得很多。

sentences.english: As you know, people in the Europe and America have been tired of wearing synthetic fabrics.
sentences.chinese: 正如你所知道的，欧美人对合成纤维织物已厌倦了。

sentences.english: This paper outlines the present situation of demand-supply and main trends of development for the World's synthetic fiber industry.
sentences.chinese: 概述世界合成纤维工业的供需现状及发展主要趋势。

sentences.english: The clothes he wears are made of synthetic fibre.
sentences.chinese: 他身上穿的那件衣服是合成纤维的。

sentences.english: This synthetic dress material does not crush.
sentences.chinese: 这种合成纤维衣料不会皱。

sentences.english: In this study, fiber modifier CM was prepared by a tertiary amine and epichlorohydrin.
sentences.chinese: 以叔胺和环氧氯丙烷为原料合成纤维改性剂CM。

sentences.english: Spinning box is an important part of the melt spinning machine for synthetic fibre.
sentences.chinese: 纺丝箱体是合成纤维熔融纺丝机中的一个重要部件。

sentences.english: Nylon and dacron are the names of synthetic fibers.
sentences.chinese: 尼龙和达克龙都是合成纤维的名称。

sentences.english: The research is mainly about the performance of synthetic fibres using in high temperature flue gas filtration.
sentences.chinese: 本课题主要研究高温烟气过滤除尘用合成纤维的性能。

sentences.english: Mainly used as polyester catalytic in the synthetic fiber industry.
sentences.chinese: 主要用于合成纤维工业作聚脂缩聚催化剂。

sentences.english: Nylon is technically described as "synthetic fiber-forming polymeric amides ."
sentences.chinese: 尼龙的技术性描述是“合成纤维的聚合氨基化合物”。

sentences.english: A single strand of untwisted synthetic fiber such as nylon used especially for fishing line .
sentences.chinese: 单丝一根未捻的合成纤维，如尼龙，尤指用于钓鱼线。

sentences.english: Synthetic fabric is inferior to cotton fabric.
sentences.chinese: 这块料子是人造棉的还是合成纤维的？

sentences.english: Polysulfonamide(PSA), a kind of high temperature resistant synthetical fibers, it is explored by national researchers.
sentences.chinese: 芳砜纶是我国自主开发的一种耐高温合成纤维。
